Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
savePowerSwitch(25.10)                                  savePowerSwitch(25.10)

Name
       savePowerSwitch  -  Stores the power switch database information, which
       can later be restored in the same floorplan through  the  restorePower-
       Switch command

Syntax
        savePowerSwitch

       [-help]

       [-outFile <string>]

       Stores  the  power  switch database information, which can later be re-
       stored in the same floorplan through the restorePowerSwitch command.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes the type  and  default
              information  for  each savePowerSwitch parameter. For a detailed
              description of the command and all its parameters, use  the  man
              command:

              man savePowerSwitch

       -outFile <string>
              Specifies  the output file for storing the power switch database
              information.

Related Information
              * addPowerSwitch

              * restorePowerSwitch

